data.description:
Welcome to elevated living in this captivating tri-level home, perfectly situated on a corner lot with mesmerizing views of Pikes Peak . This 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom gem not only offers a harmonious blend of functionality and style but also boasts a versatile flex room, setting the stage for a lifestyle of comfort and endless possibilities.  As you enter, be prepared to be enchanted by the dynamic design that seamlessly connects the multiple levels. The living area, adorned with large windows, provides an abundance of natural light, offering a warm and welcoming atmosphere for both relaxation and entertainment.

Ascend to the bedrooms, where the primary bedroom is strategically positioned to capture those gorgeous mountain views. Wake up to the awe-inspiring sight of nature's grandeur, creating a daily retreat in the comfort of your own space. The bathroom, adorned with stylish finishes, enhances the overall appeal of this tri-level haven.  But the charm doesn't stop there – a dedicated flex room awaits your personal touch. Transform it into a home office, a playroom, a fourth bedroom or a fitness studio – the choice is yours. This extra space adds an element of adaptability to suit your evolving lifestyle.

Step outside to discover the unique advantages of a corner lot, offering an expansive outdoor area for relaxation or entertainment. This tri-level sanctuary with a flex room on a corner lot is not just a home; it's an invitation to a lifestyle where functionality meets flair. Don't miss the chance to make this captivating property your own – where comfort, versatility, and mountain views converge to create a truly exceptional living experience. Panorama Park is within walking distance and you're close to schools, shopping and more!  Welcome home!
